// When the 'Sign Out' button is clicked
Function onSignOutClick():
  Attempt to sign out from Firebase
  If there is an error:
    Set 'ErrorLabel' text to the error message
  Else:
    Navigate to the 'sign up' screen

// When the 'backButton' is clicked
Function onBackButtonClick():
  Navigate to the 'profile' screen

// When the 'Reset' button is clicked
Function onResetClick():
  Attempt to reset password using the email stored in 'app variable session email'
  If there is an error:
    Set 'ErrorLabel' text to the error message
  Else:
    Set 'ErrorLabel' text to "A Password reset email has been sent to " + app variable session email
